name: Girls Blue and White Chateau Charlotte Peasant Dress
description:
What a beautiful dress for spring!

This peasant dress features a short sleeved bodice and a 2 layer full skirt. The fabric used is a hard to find cotton print called Chateau Charlotte. It features charming French country houses along with peacocks and lovebirds. Delicate white lace peeks out from bottom layer. Blue sash is included. Dress is made to be worn below the knee. All my dresses are created using French seams and top stitching for a professional quality that lasts.

Dress can be made in sizes 2 yrs to 6yrs. 

Please follow me on facebook for special sales and discounts.

name: Girls Zebra Apron and Chef Hat
description:
My child size apron and chef hat are the perfect accessory when helping mommy or daddy in the kitchen.

Apron is handcrafted from black & white zebra fabric with a contrasting hot pink & white polka dot ruffle along the bottom. To top off the apron is a hot pink daisy with a crystal center. Flower has a pin backing so it can be easily removed before washing. Apron has adjustable neck and waist ties. Chef hat is handcrafted from the same cotton fabric as the apron and is fully lined.

Chest: 6 1/2" across
Top-bottom: 20"
Widest point: 25 1/2"

Hot pink fabric may vary slightly from photo.
